extends default

block content
  p
    | Welcome to Recipe Central, your ultimate destination for discovering,
    | sharing, and enjoying delicious recipes from around the world.
    | Whether you are a beginner cook or a seasoned chef, our platform
    | offers a wealth of culinary inspiration to satisfy every palate.
    | Dive into thousands of recipes carefully curated to provide you
    | with an unforgettable cooking experience.

  p
    | At Recipe Central, we believe that food is more than just nourishment —
    | it's an experience that brings people together. Our community of passionate
    | food lovers shares their favorite dishes, cooking tips, and creative twists,
    | making this the perfect place to explore new flavors and cooking techniques.
    | Join our community today and start your culinary adventure!

  p
    | Our extensive collection of recipes is categorized by cuisine, difficulty,
    | and ingredients, ensuring that you find the perfect meal for any occasion.
    | Whether you're looking for quick weekday dinners or gourmet weekend feasts,
    | Recipe Central has got you covered. Explore classic favorites, seasonal specials,
    | and exciting international dishes that will delight your taste buds.

  p
    | We understand that every cook has unique needs and preferences, which is why
    | our recipes include detailed nutritional information, cooking times, and user reviews.
    | Plus, our easy-to-follow instructions make cooking fun and accessible for everyone.
    | From step-by-step guides to helpful cooking videos, you'll find everything you need
    | to bring your kitchen creations to life.

  p
    | At Recipe Central, we are dedicated to fostering a welcoming and inclusive community.
    | Share your own recipes, connect with fellow food enthusiasts, and discover inspiring stories
    | behind each dish. Our interactive platform makes it easy to save favorites, create
    | personalized cookbooks, and get inspired every day.

  p
    | Whether you're looking to master new skills, impress your family and friends,
    | or simply enjoy delicious meals, Recipe Central is here to support your journey.
    | We invite you to explore, experiment, and most importantly, have fun in the kitchen!